## âœ Example Twig snippet for listing:
```twig
{% for child in page.children %}
<article class="article-list-item">
  <h2>{{ child.title }}</h2>
  {% if child.media.images|first %}
    <img src="{{ child.media.images|first.url }}" alt="{{ child.title }}" />
  {% endif %}
  <p>{{ child.header.summary }}</p>
  <a href="{{ child.url }}" class="read-more">Read more</a>
</article>
{% endfor %}
```

