```

> Add CSS:
```css
.red-line {
  border: none;
  height: 3px;
  background-color: red;
  margin: 2rem 0;
}
.more-button {
  color: white;
  background: red;
  padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
  text-decoration: none;
  display: inline-block;
}
```

